-- models/fact_order_items.sql

WITH order_items AS (
    SELECT * FROM "dbt"."main"."stg_order_items"
),

order_facts AS (
    SELECT
        oi.id AS order_item_id,
        oi.order_id,
        oi.product_id,
        o.user_id,
        
    CAST(STRFTIME('%Y%m%d', o.created_at) AS INTEGER)
 AS order_date_key,
        
    CAST(STRFTIME('%Y%m%d', o.shipped_at) AS INTEGER)
 AS shipped_date_key,
        
    CAST(STRFTIME('%Y%m%d', o.delivered_at) AS INTEGER)
 AS delivered_date_key,
        
    CAST(STRFTIME('%Y%m%d', o.returned_at) AS INTEGER)
 AS returned_date_key,
        oi.sale_price,
        p.cost
    FROM order_items oi
    JOIN "dbt"."main_gold"."dim_orders" o ON oi.order_id = o.order_id
    JOIN "dbt"."main_gold"."dim_users" u ON o.user_id = u.user_id
    JOIN "dbt"."main_gold"."dim_products" p ON oi.product_id = p.product_id
)

SELECT
    order_item_id,
    order_id,
    product_id,
    user_id,
    d_order.date_key AS order_date_key,
    d_shipped.date_key AS shipped_date_key,
    d_delivered.date_key AS delivered_date_key,
    d_returned.date_key AS returned_date_key,
    sale_price,
    quantity,
    cost
FROM order_facts
JOIN "dbt"."main_gold"."dim_date" d_order ON order_facts.order_date_key = d_order.date_key
LEFT JOIN "dbt"."main_gold"."dim_date" d_shipped ON order_facts.shipped_date_key = d_shipped.date_key
LEFT JOIN "dbt"."main_gold"."dim_date" d_delivered ON order_facts.delivered_date_key = d_delivered.date_key
LEFT JOIN "dbt"."main_gold"."dim_date" d_returned ON order_facts.returned_date_key = d_returned.date_key
